# Reverse Array

The best way to reverse an array is using an in-place implementation. Meaning that you get a reference to the array and directly edit it for your reverse operations.

## Java Implementation

```java
void reverseArr(int arr[]) {
    int in = 0;
    int inl = arr.length - 1;
    while(in < inl) {
        int copy = arr[in];
        arr[in] = arr[inl];
        arr[inl] = copy;
    }
}
```

